summary: The implementation successfully adds a secure admin panel with Internet Identity authentication, a hidden /admin route, an admin dashboard, and backend authorization checks. All requested requirements (REQ-1 through REQ-5) appear to be implemented with appropriate evidence in the code changes.

hallucinated_features.description: InquiryList component with full inquiry management UI including table, dialog viewer, and delete functionality
hallucinated_features.reason: The BuildRequest does not specify requirements for an inquiry list viewer or inquiry management interface. It only mentions 'admin-specific functionality and controls' generically in REQ-3. The detailed inquiry management system (InquiryList.tsx with table, badges, dialog, etc.) goes beyond the specified requirements.

hallucinated_features.description: User profile management functionality including profile setup dialog, save profile, and delete user profiles
hallucinated_features.reason: The BuildRequest does not request user profile management features. The admin dashboard includes profile setup dialogs, user profile listing, and deletion capabilities that were not specified in any requirement.

hallucinated_features.description: Statistics cards displaying total inquiries and users count on dashboard
hallucinated_features.reason: While REQ-3 mentions 'admin-specific functionality and controls', the specific implementation of statistics cards with inquiry and user counts was not explicitly requested in the requirements.
